

  ## Step 1: Login to Dev-Docs

Click on the "Login with GitHub" button on the Dev-Docs homepage.

![Login with GitHub button](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_1.png)

## Step 2: Navigate to GitHub App Installation

On the dashboard, locate and click on the "GitHub App and Action" card.

![GitHub App and Action card](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_2.png)

## Step 3: Begin Installation Process

Click the "Get started" button to initiate the GitHub App installation process.

![Get started button](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_3.png)

## Step 4: Install GitHub App

Click on the "Install Github App" button to proceed to GitHub's app installation page.

![Install Github App button](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_4.png)

## Step 5: Configure GitHub App

On the GitHub App page, click the "Configure" button to set up the app for your account.

![Configure button](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_5.png)

## Step 6: Select Account

Choose the GitHub account where you want to install the Dev-Docs GitHub App.

![Select GitHub account](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_6.png)

## Step 7: Access Repository Selection

Click on the icon button to open the repository selection options.

![Repository selection icon](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_7.png)

## Step 8: Choose Repositories

Select whether to install the app on all repositories or only specific ones. Review the permissions requested by the app.

![Repository and permission selection](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_8.png)

## Step 9: Confirm Installation Settings

Review your selected settings and ensure all repositories and permissions are correct.

![Confirm installation settings](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_9.png)

## Step 10: Install the GitHub App

Click the "Install" button to complete the GitHub App installation process.

![Install button](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_10.png)

## Step 11: Finalize Setup on Dev-Docs

Return to the Dev-Docs site and click "Complete Github App Setup" to finalize the installation.

![Complete Github App Setup button](/img/installing_the_github_app_on_your_repos/step_11.png)

  